\f2\fs29\fsmilli14667 In a real-world scenario, you will not calculate these metrics one by one. The Python library 
\f0\b Pandas
\f2\b0  provides a single function that instantly calculates all descriptive statistics for every numerical column in your dataset.
\f1\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li960\fi-960\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 import pandas as pd
